# Spec Sync

When making changes to domain logic (events, entities, derived state, pages):

1. Check `spec/diagram/events.puml` and `entities.puml` — update if adding/removing event types or entity types
2. Check `spec/features/` — update or create `.feature` files if adding new user-facing actions or changing existing behavior
3. Spec changes should be committed alongside the code changes, not as a separate step
